Chris wrote:

>>I would suggest using a dome light bulb in series with the battery
>to see if it is a large load (bright light) b/c most of the $20 multimeters 
>would let the smoke out if subjected to a 5 AMP load in the current meter 
>setting.
>
>If the bulb is bright, big load, if the bulb doesn't light or is very dim 
>you might be okay testing it with the meter.
